1021001.name: Bunny Plushie
1021001.description: A pink stuffed bunny with a scarf. It's made of soft materials that make you want to hug it all day.

1021002.name: Romantic's Bouquet
1021002.description: This bouquet exudes a rich, captivating aroma. Both the roses and the other red flowers are practically dripping with emotion and romance.

1021003.name: Cake Gift Box
1021003.description: A meticulously wrapped box containing slices of delicious cake. You can eat them yourself, or you can gift them and make someone's day.

1051701.name: Crystal Candy
1051701.description: The transparent glass jar is full of shiny, colorful candy. When you open the lid, you smell the sweet scent of bliss.

1990301.name: Heart in Crayon
1990301.description: An adorably colored canvas that seems to capture all of Anchorage's world within. Every line reflects her innocence.

1990302.name: Elegant Frame
1990302.description: A union of wavy ribbons and a wooden frame - a point where color and inspiration converge. Her creativity blooms with a burst of joy.

2022001.name:
Cleaning Supplies
Toolbox
2022001.description: A toolbox of must-have items for cleaning and tidying up both at home and at the workplace. It's built with durable and resilient materials to protect the tools inside from damage.

2022002.name: Royal Tea Set
2022002.description:
A classy, elegant tea set from the Royal Islands.
Its blue and white design feels both refreshing and relaxing, bringing grace to your teatime.

2022003.name:
The Perfect Maid's
Guidebook
2022003.description:
This book explains in detail the knowledge, skills, and mindset that a perfect maid must have, using examples and thought-out theory.
It urges the reader to carry the spirit of maidly service with them even in daily life.

3022101.name: Sincere Loafers
3022101.description:
A simple design with a simple color scheme. Easy and comfortable to wear. 
They fit perfectly around the heel and welcome your feet every time you put them on.

3022102.name: Foot Massager
3022102.description: Relieve your stress, soothe your mind, and feel your body's energy return to you!

3070701.name: Love Enshackled
3070701.description: Handcuffs with a heart charm between them, simple yet profound. The cool touch of metal conveys a loving bond like nothing else.

4990501.name: Tulip Glass
4990501.description:
A lovely, elegant glass resembling a rosebud beneath the dawnlight.
Within its curves, the memories of two people tenderly intermingle and coalesce.
